ter my death.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE OREE-DO AN ATA-ZAW-WAJA FA QADDIR LEE MENAN NESAAA-E A-O’FE-HUNNA FAR-JAN WA AH-FAZE-HUNNA LEE FEE NAFSE-HAA WA AW-SA-E’HUNNA LEE RIZQAN WA A’ZAME-HUN LEE BARA-KATAN FEE NAFSE-HAA WA MAA LEE FA-QADDIR LEE MIN-HAA WALA-DAN TAIYYE-BAN TAJ-A’LO-HU KHALA-FAN SAALE-HAN FEE HAYAA-TEE WA BAA’DA MAWTEE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اُرِیْدُ اَنْ اَتَزَوَّجَ فَقَدِّرْ لِیْ مِنَ النِّسَاۗئِ اَعُفِهُنَّ فَرْجًا وَاَحْفَظِهُنَّ لِیْ فِیْ نَفْسِهَا وَاَوْسَعِهُنَّ لِیْ رِزْقًا وَاَعْظَمِهُنْ لِیْ بَرَكَۃً فِیْ نَفْسِهَا وَمَا لِیْ فَقَدِّرْ لِیْ مِنْهَا وَلَدًا طَیِّبًا تَجْعَلُهٗ خَلَفًا صَالِحًا فِیْ حَیَاتِیْ وَبَعْدَ مَوْتِیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSig